<span class="subhead">TOP TECHNOLOGY POLICY OFFICIALS JOIN INTERNATIONAL SUPERSESSION AT THE  2008 INTERNATIONAL CES </span><br>
The Consumer 

Electronics Association (CEA)<sup>&#174</sup> today announced that senior  technology 

policymakers from the European Union, Japan  and the United States  will participate in an 

International SuperSession at the 2008 International CES<sup>&#174</sup>.  Produced by CEA, the 

2008  International CES, the world&rsquo;s largest consumer technology tradeshow, is scheduled  

