International CES - the  world&rsquo;s largest consumer technology tradeshow. These exhibiting companies  represent more than 30 different consumer 

technology categories, including emerging  technologies, gaming hardware and software and digital imaging.<br>
<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11415">Read all about it</a><br><br>

<span class="subhead">NORTHEAST TECHNOLOGY COMPANIES MAKE IMPACT AT THE 2008 INTERNATIONAL CES</span><br>
250 technology companies from the Northeast region of  the United States  will showcase their latest consumer electronics products at the 2008  International CES, the world&rsquo;s largest consumer technology tradeshow. Together,  these exhibitors make the northeastern U.S. the second most represented  domestic region at CES and cover more than 30 consumer technology categories.<br>
<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11414">Read all about it</a><br><br>

<span class="subhead">MIDWEST TECHNOLOGY COMPANIES INCREASE PRESENCE AT THE 2008 INTERNATIONAL CES</span><br>
