<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11410">Read all about it</a><br><br>

<span class="subhead">MID-ATLANTIC TECHNOLOGY COMPANIES GENERATE INDUSTRY BUZZ AT THE 2008 INTERNATIONAL CES</span><br>
More than 125 technology companies from the Mid-Atlantic  region of the United States  will showcase their latest consumer electronics products at the 2008  International CES - the world&rsquo;s largest consumer technology tradeshow. These  exhibiting companies represent more than 30 consumer technology categories,  including emerging technologies, gaming hardware and software and digital  imaging.<br>
<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11408">Read all about it</a><br><br>

