Association (CEA)<sup>&#174</sup>  today announced that Cisco Systems Chairman  and CEO John 

Chambers will deliver a keynote address at the Leaders in  Technology Dinner, to be held at the 

2008 International CES. <br>
<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11401">Read all about it</a><br><br>

