Association  (CEA)<sup>&#174</sup> and Parents&rsquo; Choice Foundation today announced the 

creation  of the <strong><em>Sandbox Summit:  A Playdate With Technology.</em></strong> The 

conference and exhibition will debut at  the 2008 International CES<sup>&#174</sup> in Las   

 Vegas, running from January 7 to 10, 2008.<br>
<a href="/press/news/rd_release_detail.asp?id=11385">Read all about it</a><br><br>

